@Web_HostAddress = http://localhost:5135

### Health
GET {{Web_HostAddress}}/

### Single transaction ingestion
POST {{Web_HostAddress}}/ingest/transaction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "C1",
  "transactionDate": "2024-01-01T12:00:00Z",
  "amount": 10.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "sourceChannel": "web"
}

### Customer transactions
GET {{Web_HostAddress}}/customers/C1/transactions?page=1&pageSize=50&currency=USD

### Stats
GET {{Web_HostAddress}}/stats/summary
